i-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Our\r\nservices are based on 3 major points: </span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Experience:</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">An excellent reputation for personal\r\nservices, quality and value through extensive research and a comprehensive\r\ndatabase backed up by twenty years of experience in the travel industry.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Our agents travel to the places\r\nthey sell on a regular basis. They inspect the newest properties along with\r\nolder properties that have undergone renovation.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We feel this is an extremely\r\nimportant aspect of being an above average travel consultant. It is what\r\nenables us to suggest properties that match our client\'s needs, and\r\npersonalities. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Service:<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Professional customer-oriented\r\nconsultation providing hassle free travel. Email capabilities for convenience\r\nand prompt booking and information. Creative but persistent approach to search\r\nfor the most appropriate travel arrangements and identifying the best possible\r\nvalue. Our travel consultants are friendly, professional, and experienced in\r\naccommodating both the seasoned traveler and those new to the world of travel.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We pride ourselves in customer\r\nsatisfaction. A large percentage of our bookings are from repeat clientele\r\nwhile much of our new business is from word of mouth recommendations. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Value:\r\n</span></b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">With our “Know How “, and as a\r\nsales agent for almost all major international airlines in Jordan, we do not\r\nonly offer competitive prices to our customer, but we are also able to pass on\r\nvery competitive prices and a maximum opportunity for choices and flexibility.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">These three points are\r\nrepresented in our logo, the first sunbeam on the left is the deepest\r\nrepresenting Experience as we believe it is our base, the second sunbeam in the\r\ncenter represents Service, as we believe it is the center and the core of our\r\nbusiness, the highes