d to:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Pre-planning\r\nand approval</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Supplier\r\nsourcing and contract management Attendee management</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Transportation</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Accommodations</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">On-site\r\noperations</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Payment\r\nand reconciliation Risk management</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l1 level1 lfo5\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">v<span style=\"font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Performance\r\nmeasurement</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Team\r\nBuilding: </span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We provide effective and\r\nwell-organized team building through expert facilitation. Our team provides\r\nvalue added services to Employers and Employees of different industries.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We pride ourselves in the type of\r\nservices we render our clients, these includes:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Finding the right location for\r\nyour team building,</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Transport to the location\r\n(ticketing if needed),</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Accommodation/\r\nhotel booking,</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Providing you with exceptional\r\nfacilitators (Experienced and trained for the business)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Entertainment e.g. DJs, band and\r\nMCs</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Conferences:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We have the experience,\r\nexpertise, and capacity to handle conferences of all sizes, ranging from a\r\nsmall group of 10 to thousands of participants locally, regionally and\r\ninternationally.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Our experience combined with our\r\ninnovative Strategy will allow us to provide your company with unparalleled\r\nservice in planning your next meeting or event.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">If you have meeting planners, we\r\nwill work with them to coordinate all the logistics, assist with budgeting and\r\nhelp organize attendees.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">CWT Kenya goes the extra mile to\r\nensure your speakers and guests are treated like VIP’s and we strive for\r\nexcellence to make each event a success.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Visa,\r\nPassport Handling &amp; Immigration Services</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Our Visa &amp; Immigration\r\nDepartment works closely with our Travel Consultants to ensure information is\r\nrelayed to our clients as soon as it is available from the Embassy. At the time\r\nof ticket reservation, our Travel Consultants will relay all visa requirements\r\nfor that particular travel specifying the duration of visa processing as well\r\nas the visa application forms required for completion. During the embassy\r\nprocessing time, our Visa tracking officer keeps an electronic visa log for all\r\nthe visas that have been launched and the expected completion date vis-à-vis\r\nthe client’s traveling date. With this, a quality check will always be done to\r\navoid any inconveniences to our travelers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">CWT Kenya has a great working\r\nrelationship with the Kenyan Immigration Department, which gives us a wealth of\r\nexperience and the capacity to provide services such as:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Work Permits</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Dependent Passes</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Alien Card Registration</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Special Passes</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Cancellation of permits and\r\npasses</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Endorsement of passports</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Processing of all passes</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Travel Insurance</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">We recommend Travel Insurance\r\nduring travel to deal with unexpected emergencies. We strive to provide the\r\nbest and most flexible travel insurance services to all our clients. Through\r\nour local partner we offer travel insurance that covers various travel-related\r\nemergencies and we will not charge any facilitation fee, but you will be\r\nrequired to pay the actual insurance costs you choose to take.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Travel\r\nInsurance to cover the following risks: </span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Medical Expenses</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Personal Accident Cover</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Premature Return in Case of Death\r\nor Imminent Death of Relative Or Business Associate</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Legal Assistance Abroad</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Terrorism</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Cancellation or Curtailment\r\nCovers</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Hi-Jack – Public Conveyance</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Kidnap and Wrongful Detention</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">Safari related incidents</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Georgia&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n');
