nt-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">WHO\r\nWE ARE<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex Labour hiring &amp; Cleaning Services Limited\r\nwas founded by individuals with in-depth knowledge of Labour hiring &amp; cleaning\r\nindustry with a goal of providing unparalleled customer service to multiple\r\nclienteles. Fueled by a desire to raise standards in the industry, the company\r\nhas an anticipation of growing to become one of leaders in Labour hiring &amp;\r\ncleaning industry to reckon with, it has the potential to provide excellent Labour\r\nhiring Employee &amp; cleaning services with an intention of meeting ever\r\nevolving needs of the diverse clientele.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex Labour hiring &amp; cleaning services limited\r\nhas already gained high-quality reputation as optimum quality contract cleaning\r\ncompany engaged in basic and advanced level of cleaning services with multi\r\nmodel features and management services. From commercial sectors, industrial,\r\nconstruction and residential, professionals are here to offer reliable and\r\nhonest services in a row. <b>‘</b>We build\r\nlong term relationships by providing an excellent service delivered through our\r\nvalued and highly trained team<b>’.<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Our clients benefits from a bespoke service that is\r\ntailored to each customer’s needs. We use environmentally friendly cleaning\r\nmaterials that all our employees have been trained on and there use, our health\r\n&amp; safety record is impeccable. Our employees are the key to our successful\r\nand growing business. Careful selection, training and support are of upper most\r\nimportance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom