e-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">WHAT\r\nMAKES US DIFFERENT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Customer service and training are real problems for\r\nthe Unilex cleaning and labour hiring company and our company aspires to raise\r\nthese to new heights, requiring extremely strict training requirements and\r\nproviding excellent and fast customer service with no turnaround time. These\r\ntwo areas are sadly lacking, and may lead to labour hiring and cleaning\r\nproblems. Our emphasis are given on the site training and orientation support\r\nwhen needed, and first aid training. Contact numbers are available at all\r\ntimes, and the employee are trained in when and how to use these numbers if\r\nnecessary. We are different because we offer excellent customer service\r\ntogether with excellent training and services.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex difference is in the details. We take the time\r\nto understand the challenges that our clients are facing, and then we assist in\r\ndeveloping a good program that works for their unique budget.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex is an extremely innovative company that is\r\nalways open to fresh ideas. We are always looking at new ways to improve our\r\noperations.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex difference lies in our depth of knowledge. It\r\ncan also be found in our exemplary customer service and follow up. It’s evident\r\nin our stringent personnel selection process and how we subsequently invest\r\nheavily in to our staffs training, support, supervision and personal\r\ndevelopment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Finally, unilex difference is in our attitude. In\r\nevery interaction with you, our single purpose is to forge a relationship\r\nexceeding all of your expectations<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-fareast