an></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex It is a limited company that was formed to\r\nsource jobs for highly qualified and experienced job seekers, with the aim of\r\nmatching companies with the highly qualified staff. We are registered with the\r\nMinistry of Labour to offer recruitment services both locally and\r\ninternationally. We are also recognized by the Ministry of Foreign Affairs in\r\nas far as international recruitment is concerned. We are also certified by the\r\nKenya Chamber of Commerce and Industry and also the Kenya Association of\r\nPrivate Employment Agencies (KAPEA) effectively and efficiently manages you\r\nlabour based on your needs; Taking care of all day-to-day labour and tax\r\nmatters<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Supply competent staff managed by us from our payroll\r\nat your request, giving priority to those recommend by the client<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">We will remove headcount cost from your balance sheet.\r\nOffering quick and cost effective services to the clients. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:red;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Electrical Works<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">We undertake all the essential electrical and\r\nhousehold mechanical works and we are the only facility management entity to\r\nalso provide electrical maintenance contracts, which are especially designed\r\nand specifically dedicated for the house and offices etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><v:rect id=\"Rectangle_x0020_448\" o:spid=\"_x0000_s2061\" style=\"position:absolute;\r\n left:0;text-align:left;margin-left:0;margin-top:-171.7pt;width:57.75pt;\r\n height:859pt;z-index:-251650560;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square;\r\n mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent:0;mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right:9pt;\r\n mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:left;\r\n mso-position-horizontal-relative:page;mso-position-vertical:absolute;\r\n mso-position-vertical-relative:text;mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent:0;\r\n mso-width-relative:page;mso-height-relative:page;v-text-anchor:top\" o:gfxdata=\"UEsDBBQABgAIAAAAIQC75UiUBQEAAB4CAAATAAAAW0NvbnRlbnRfVHlwZXNdLnhtbKSRvU7DMBSF\r\ndyTewfKKEqcMCKEmHfgZgaE8wMW+SSwc27JvS/v23KTJgkoXFsu+P+c7Ol5vDoMTe0zZBl/LVVlJ\r\ngV4HY31Xy4/tS3EvRSbwBlzwWMsjZrlprq/W22PELHjb51r2RPFBqax7HCCXIaLnThvSAMTP1KkI\r\n+gs6VLdVdad08ISeCho1ZLN+whZ2jsTzgcsnJwldluLxNDiyagkxOquB2Knae/OLUsyEkj