margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:red;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">HEALTH\r\nAND SAFETY STATEMENT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:150%;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">This statement should be read in conjunction with the\r\nHealth &amp; Safety policies that set out specific responsibilities and\r\narrangements by which Health &amp; Safety is to be organized, implemented and\r\nmonitored within the company.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.25pt;mso-font-width:99%;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex Cleaning\r\nServices Limited is committed to providing a healthy and safe working\r\nenvironment for all employees and non-employees affected by our activities. We\r\nwill use all reasonable endeavors to ensure safe systems of work throughout our\r\nbusiness activities, and will do all that is reasonably practicable to ensure a\r\nsafe &amp; healthy working environment and safe working methods.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.25pt;mso-font-width:99%;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Unilex Cleaning\r\nServices considers that health &amp; safety an important part of all our\r\nmanagement systems and that clear communication and co-operation between management,\r\nemployees and the client is important in order to achieve a high standard of\r\nhealth &amp; safety at work.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.25pt;mso-font-width:99%;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">General\r\npolicymaking is the responsibility of the Directors, the major objective being\r\nto promote correct standards of health, safety and welfare that comply with the\r\nHealth and Safety at Work Act 2007 and all other statutory provisions and codes\r\nof practice.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.25pt;mso-font-width:99%;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">The company will:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.35pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo1;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">a)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Initiate and maintain a safe and healthy workplace, so\r\nfar as is reasonably practicable, to ensure that employees, customers, visitors\r\nand the environment are not exposed to risks arising from our cleaning\r\nactivities.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:37.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-12.35pt;\r\nline-height:150%;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo1;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:\r\nnone\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nletter-spacing:-.05pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US\">b)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-language:EN-US\">Ensure that employees have adequate support,\r\nsupervision, relevant health &amp; safety documentation, information and\r\ntraining required, in order to make them aware of potential hazards within the\r\nworkplace.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;mar